canadian seafar threaten strike canadian seafar are almost certain to go on strike thi spring in a refu to meet rollback in wage and benefit ask for by their employ , seafar ' intern union offici roman gralewicz said . `` it 's 99.9 percent -- i guarant you a strike , `` gralewicz said in an interview . the union repr about 2,300 worker on the great lake and canada 's east and west coast . contract talk broke off in januari and a concili ha been appoint to tri to help settl the disput . the current contract expir at the end of march . the seafar ' employ are also ask for a reduct in crew level , a move which the union said would cost about 400 job .